{"tid":2205190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"導演Judd Apatow表示荷里活為錢對中國沉默","createTime":"2020-09-16T15:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T16:57:30.000Z","uid":157092,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"823212edcbb3e98e30c897d8d897d38b8c8afad1","tid":2205190,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"Twitter link <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IndieWire/status/1306239380416278530?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndieWire%2Fstatus%2F1306239380416278530%3Fs%3D19&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=36c13e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndieWire%2Fstatus%2F1306239380416278530%3Fs%3D19&h=9b7f79ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/IndieWire/status/1306239380416278530?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\nIndiewire 原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/judd-apatow-hollywood-censoring-films-china-1234586770/amp/?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fjudd-apatow-hollywood-censoring-films-china-1234586770%2Famp%2F%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=cd32fec4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/judd-apatow-hollywood-censoring-films-china-1234586770/amp/?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄:<br />\n&ldquo;A lot of these giant corporate entities have business with countries around the world, Saudi Arabia or China, and they&rsquo;re just not going to criticize them,&rdquo; Apatow said, &ldquo;and they&rsquo;re not going to let their shows criticize them or they&rsquo;re not going to air documentaries that go deep into truthful areas because they make so much money.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nApatow added, &ldquo;So while we&rsquo;re going, &lsquo;Can we say this joke, can we not say that joke,&rsquo; on a much bigger level, they have just completely shut down critical content about human rights abuses in China, and I think that&rsquo;s much scarier.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAs an example, the &ldquo;Knocked Up&rdquo; and &ldquo;King of Staten Island&rdquo; director said studios would shoot him down if he ever pitched a movie about a man who escapes Chinese concentration camps, referring to the imprisonment of Muslim Uighurs in China&rsquo;s Xinjiang province. Disney has recently come under fire for filming part of its live-action &ldquo;Mulan&rdquo; film in Xinjiang and using the film&rsquo;s end credits to thank &ldquo;the publicity department of CPC Xinjiang Uighur Autonomy Region Committee.&rdquo; Over one million Uighur Muslims have reportedly been detained in the region."},{"pid":"be9e820a9e3b5da93ea5006c37043861908c5882","tid":2205190,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b773d74290d1afa60a56c9128f50c768866289","tid":2205190,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb66444814188b9d9e95561b935b8bafc727363","tid":2205190,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"佢好似專拍鳩戲 <br />\n<br />\n不過respect"},{"pid":"d054fb27404e1401d46c2ab9fd965c68b2029c70","tid":2205190,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cla